{"tid":184362,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人聽過林二汶既《無忘花》？","createTime":"2017-04-02T17:36:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-03T05:44:25.000Z","uid":4260,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"acd5861af6385dee1a574459eebb7efe5513cbc2","tid":184362,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T17:36:02.000Z","msg":"在生命轉了一圈回到起點時 只希望能留住最好的回憶<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林二汶 Eman Lam - 《無忘花》官方 MV <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=x_LC5ds_oYk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dx_LC5ds_oYk&d=1bJdDSIrk6tBa%2BBM68SGejA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=5f68b820\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=x_LC5ds_oYk</a>"},{"pid":"2cb2d4ab32635b5e88f1a8e93226185851361284","tid":184362,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T17:36:15.000Z","msg":"曲詞：林一峰@LYFE<br />\n編曲：何秉舜@goomusic<br />\n監製：何秉舜@goomusic<br />\n<br />\n如果失重兩肩感慨萬千<br />\n太累沒法可入眠<br />\n你能讓眉頭積雪<br />\n落到我手心裏<br />\n無忘花又再現<br />\n<br />\n我清楚你的心一切弱點<br />\n有誰讓你數心跳<br />\n愛如願隨年轉厚<br />\n換你回贈一吻<br />\n度四季於一笑<br />\n<br />\n花田遇上了春暖<br />\n花瓣夏雨灑風中轉<br />\n百折千廻就放開 秋色染面<br />\n老情人 心照不宣<br />\n冬雪會倦情感會亂<br />\n睡醒已是明天<br />\n仍期待下一花季可再見<br />\n<br />\n情深不見底不必怕緣淺<br />\n會承受你的改變<br />\n我從未要你解釋 沒有名份的吻<br />\n無忘花枝不需折<br />\n<br />\n花笑獨欠人不見<br />\n不記明日黃花昨日現<br />\n百折千廻 時日流轉不了斷<br />\n好情人 有聚有別<br />\n總可再遇抱擁每段<br />\n再想已是明天<br />\n長留在我心的你不會變<br />\n<br />\n愛如願隨年轉厚<br />\n換你回贈一吻<br />\n度四季於一天"},{"pid":"5110dcb1e7d8c1b35b21e37e13c6816f6654ab34","tid":184362,"uid":98735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T17:40:53.000Z","msg":"琴晚聽左攪屎棍既cover<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45cfb09f8debe2f716888733299d8351ce5beb8c","tid":184362,"uid":54576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T17:43:09.000Z","msg":"林二汶